# Ankuram Tuition Centre - Website Project Rules

## Brand
- Name: Ankuram Tuition Centre
- Location: Jubilee Hills, Hyderabad
- Phone: 7396669430
- Tagline: "Foundations First. Results Follow."

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 14 with App Router
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- Static export (output: 'export' in next.config)

## Design Guidelines
- Premium, minimalist, typography-driven
- No stock photos — use icons, gradients, geometric patterns, whitespace
- Mobile-first responsive design
- Colors: Deep navy (#0f1d3d), Accent blue (#1e40af), White, Light gray (#f8fafc)
- Fonts: System fonts (Inter or similar sans-serif)
- Cards with subtle borders, not heavy shadows

## CTAs (Every Page)
- Primary: "Schedule Diagnostic Assessment" → WhatsApp link (https://wa.me/917396669430?text=Hi%20I%20want%20to%20book%20a%20diagnostic%20assessment)
- Secondary: "Call Us" → tel:+917396669430
- No contact forms anywhere

## Content Rules
- Speak to parents, not students
- Tone: Confident, empathetic, professional — not salesy
- Highlight: diagnostic-first approach, small batches (3-5), 13+ years experience
- Never include Swastik's educational background (degrees, colleges, Amazon) on the website

## SEO
- Every page must have unique title, meta description, H1
- Add FAQ schema on pages that have FAQs
- Add LocalBusiness schema on homepage
- Semantic HTML throughout

## File Structure
- Pages in /app directory
- Reusable components in /components
- Keep components modular and reusable
